      "originalText": "Architecture: Microservices with message-oriented middleware\nCommunication: gRPC (synchronous RPC) between services\nCoordination: Bully algorithm for leader election among executor replicas\nFailure Model: Crash-stop (processes may crash, no Byzantine behavior)\nVector Clocks: [TransactionVerif, FraudDetect, Suggestions] — 3 services,\n                        7 events (A-G) tracking causal ordering across validation workflow\nReplication: 3 order executor replicas for high availability\nFault Tolerance: Automatic re-election when leader crashes\nScalability: Horizontal scaling via Docker Compose replicas",
      "autoResize": true,
