    {
      "id": "failure-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 122.68061919544596,
      "y": -332.33828187783894,
      "width": 411.7494591562691,
      "height": 58.821351308038444,
      "fontSize": 10.083660224235162,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. Service Crash: Leader election triggers new leader automatically\n2. Network Partition: Heartbeat timeout (3s) → re-election via Bully algorithm\n3. Queue Full: Orders buffer in memory (in-memory deque, bounded)\n4. Message Loss: gRPC timeout (2-3s) → retry or fail-fast to client",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 64,
